2
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:08,060
Well, that's the last
of it, Filthy Rich.

3
00:00:08,270 --> 00:00:13,485
Just Rich, please. And on behalf
of Rich's Barnyard Bargains,

4
00:00:13,510 --> 00:00:17,090
thanks for another season's
shipment of Zap Apple Jam.

5
00:00:17,425 --> 00:00:19,265
Our pleasure. See
ya next time!

6
00:00:22,820 --> 00:00:26,445
Uh, Apple Bloom? Did you pack up
the cider into the same crates

7
00:00:26,470 --> 00:00:27,915
as the Zap Apple Jam?

8
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,420
Sure did! Now that
I'm getting older,

9
00:00:30,505 --> 00:00:33,885
I want to prove I can handle
more responsibility on the farm.

10
00:00:34,050 --> 00:00:35,815
But the crates aren't marked.

11
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:38,650
You kept track of what when
into which crate, right?

12
00:00:39,055 --> 00:00:43,755
Oh. Um... Yep. I totally
kept track of everything.

13
00:00:44,755 --> 00:00:47,745
Good. Because we wouldn't want
Filthy Rich to get a shipment

14
00:00:47,765 --> 00:00:50,675
of cider when he's supposed
to get Zap Apple Jam.

15
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:53,225
You know how Granny
feels about selling cider

16
00:00:53,255 --> 00:00:54,610
anywhere but
on the farm.

17
00:00:55,015 --> 00:00:57,195
Are you sure he
got the right crates?

18
00:00:58,190 --> 00:00:59,440
Sure, I'm sure!

19
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:02,820
Now why don't you and Big
Mac head on out to the house

20
00:01:02,865 --> 00:01:04,290
and let me finish up here!

21
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:10,810
If you gave Rich the Zap Apple
Jam, then what's this here?

22
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:13,330
Um... Extra?

23
00:01:13,805 --> 00:01:15,145
Nnope!

24
00:01:15,735 --> 00:01:18,550
